Hello Rafaella,
Today's visit was successful, and we made good progress on drafting the sco=
pe for the repairs. We were onsite for an hour and a half.
There are a couple of areas upstairs where we would like to cut away some g=
ib board linings on the external walls to have an exploratory look inside t=
he wall cavities to check to see that there is no smoke contamination in th=
ose areas.
I would also like to get David's team to commence with the next phase of cl=
eaning to the upstairs level.
Can I please have your permission for Davids team to commence with the comm=
ercial cleaning to the mid floor level of the property tomorrow? This is th=
e next step in the process.
Many Thanks,
Grant.


[cid:image001.png@01DC0AD9.D96D9250]
Grant Metson
Regional Manager - House Assessing
Phone 021 744 288
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street,
PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142

